dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Peter Torres. May I ask for your name?
Nice to meet you, Sharon! Can you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six two three eight and my date of birth is zero five slash one four slash one nine seven eight.
Thank you, Sharon. I have verified your information. Can you also confirm your current address and contact number for our records?
My address is two zero one Park Avenue, and my contact number is triple eight five five six two one zero.
Great, thank you for providing that, Sharon. Is there anything specific you would like assistance with today regarding your auto insurance policy?
I just wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, I can assist you with that. Thank you for reaching out, Sharon. If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. Have a great day!
